description: Returns the current onboarding status of the telemetry config feature, including the status of the feature and reason the feature failed to start or stop.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The onboarding status of the telemetry config feature.

nested_items.name: FailureReason
nested_items.description: Describes the reason for the failure status. The field will only be populated if Status is FAILED_START or FAILED_STOP.
